lead_paragraph: Europe is sending out some heavy metal to start the Ryder Cup — Justin Rose and his Olympic gold with Henrik Stenson and his silver claret jug.

headline.print_headline: Europe Sends Out Its Heavy (Olympic) Medal at Ryder Cup
